      <mod loc="c57-0090__main__d1e14838__End"/> I now <lb/> viewed. But the recollection of those days <lb/> was too painful; I must shut out all <lb/> thought to enjoy tranquillity, &amp; that <lb/> reflection alone is sufficient to poison <lb/> every pleasure.<milestone unit="tei:p"/><add loc="c57-0090__main__d1e14859__Start"/><metamark function="paragraph">[</metamark><add loc="c57-0090__main__d1e14859__End"/> At Cologne we descended <lb/> to the plains of Holland &amp; we resolved to <lb/> post the remainder of our way for <lb/> the wind was contrary &amp; the stream of <lb/> the river was too gentle to aid us. We now <lb/> arrived at very different country. The <lb/> soil was sandy and the wheels sunk deep <lb/> in it. The towns of th<mod loc="c57-0090__main__d1e14878__Start"/>
